        "text": "Effect [ edit | edit source ] Mortal Spin inflicts damage and then removes any binding effects and Leech Seed from the user, as well as entry hazards from the user's side of the field (unless the user has fainted as a result of the move, such as from Rough Skin ). It also leaves each target poisoned . In a battle with multiple opponents, it will target all adjacent opponents. Affected moves [ edit | edit source ] The following moves are affected by Mortal Spin: Move Type Cat. Bind Normal Physical Fire Spin Fire Special Infestation Bug Special Leech Seed Grass Status Magma Storm Fire Special Sand Tomb Ground Physical Snap Trap Grass Physical Spikes Ground Status Stealth Rock Rock Status Sticky Web Bug Status Toxic Spikes Poison Status Whirlpool Water Special Wrap Normal Physical",
